What you need to know:

He played for the brewers from 2016 to 2020 and also turned up for Western Stima for six months before moving to Gor Mahia in August. At Stima, under the tutelage of coach Salim Babu, the defensive midfielder scored four goals and was a regular starter for the KPL side.The former Kisumu Day student nurtured his talent as Kisumu's Palos FC before his stint with Tusker and Western Stima.